title: Share of the population who gave to charity in England 2019 , by age
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of respondents, containing a total of 6 data points.
In general Share of respondents has rose over the Year.
Share of respondents is slightly increasing from 16_to_24 to 35_to_49, and finally roughly constant from 35_to_49 to 75_and_over.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 16_to_24 and 25_to_34.
The highest Share of respondents, of value 83.0 was reached at Year 75_and_over
The lowest Share of respondents, of value 59.0 was reported at Year 16_to_24
